SnapATAC : Embedding

set.seed(1)

addTimeStamp <- function(saveInfo, tstart, info){
  timeDiff <- abs(round(difftime(Sys.time(), tstart, units = "mins"), 3))
  print(paste0("Adding Time Stamp : ", info, ", ", timeDiff, " minutes from start..."))
  saveInfo$timeStamps[[length(saveInfo$timeStamps) + 1]] <- list(
    info = info, 
    time = timeDiff
  )
  saveInfo
}

  threads <- floor(params$threads / 2)
}else{
  threads <- 1
}

#2. UMAP Embedding
snapObj <- runViz(
    obj=snapObj, 
    tmp.folder=tempdir(),
    dims=2,
    eigs.dims=1:20, 
    method="umap",
    num.cores = threads,
    seed.use=10
  )
saveInfo <- addTimeStamp(saveInfo, tstart, info = "runUMAP")
## [1] "Adding Time Stamp : runUMAP, 4.43 minutes from start..."
#3. Plot Embedding
plotViz(
    obj=snapObj,
    method="umap", 
    main=paste0(params$project, " Samples"),
    point.color=snapObj@sample, 
    point.size=1, 
    point.shape=19, 
    point.alpha=0.8, 
    text.add=TRUE,
    text.size=1.5,
    text.color="black",
    text.halo.add=TRUE,
    text.halo.color="white",
    text.halo.width=0.2,
    down.sample=10^9,
    legend.add=FALSE
  )
